Treasure hunt
engine to online treasure hunt games.
(Created first for tresor chasse, Conjura'11)

Copy and paste the config.php.sample as config.php and add the username
password for the database

To register admin user place the firstReg.php in the folder and 
firstReg.php?name=<admin_user>&password=<admin_password>

Make sure you delete the firstReg.php file after it's use.. 

Adding Levels.
--------------

Input the Level name as the level number.
The first level should be started from level 0.

EDIT: Plan to redesign it based on some framework..
